Package org.eclipse.e4.core.services.log

Class Logger

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.e4.core.services.log.Logger
public abstract class Logger extends Object
Logging warnings, errors, information, as well as capturing debug and trace information. Everything done through this interface is not meant for normal end users. Strings are not expected to be translated.
